6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to antipsychotic drugs; amending 56
O.S. 2021, Section 204, which relates to vendor drug
8 program; authorizing the Oklahoma Health Care
Authority to approve prior authorized antipsychotics;
9 providing for certain disorders; establishing certain
prior authorization; and providing an effective date.
